data.description: Array with one row per combination of dimension values.

dimensions.description: Array of dimension values, representing the combination of dimension values corresponding to this row.

data_lag.description: Number of seconds between current time and last processed event, in another words how many seconds of data could be missing.

max.description: Maximum results for each metric (object mapping metric names to values). Currently always an empty object.

min.description: Minimum results for each metric (object mapping metric names to values). Currently always an empty object.

filters.description: Segmentation filter in 'attribute operator value' format.

since.description: Start date and time of requesting data period in ISO 8601 format.

sort.description: Array of dimensions to sort by, where each dimension may be prefixed by - (descending) or + (ascending).

items.description: Dimension name (may be prefixed by - (descending) or + (ascending).

until.description: End date and time of requesting data period in ISO 8601 format.

rows.description: Total number of rows in the result.

totals.description: Total results for metrics across all data (object mapping metric names to values).
